About this item

    This fits your .

  • USB C to Micro USB charge and sync cable enables you to connect a USB C equipped laptop to Micro USB equipped devices (smartphones, tablets, game controllers, power banks, Bluetooth headphones, cameras, etc.). Plug and play, no dongles or adapters needed;
  • Broad Compatibility: this cable is compatible with all laptops that equipped with USB-C female port, such as Macbook 2015, MacBook Pro 2016, Chromebook Pixel, ASUS Zen AiO, ThinkPad New S2, ThinkPad T570, Alienware 17, YOGA 900, HUAWEI MateBook, HP Pavilion x2 , HP Spectre x2 and so on; USB C is compatible with thunderbolt 3;
  • Universal Practicality: the USB C to Micro B cable could connect Macbook Pro or other Type-C laptops to Android phone or tablet for charging and syncing, widely compatible with most Android devices, such as Galaxy S7 S6 S5 Edge, Note 5 4 3, Nexus 6P, Galaxy Tab S3, Huawei MediaPad M3; and xbox one controller, PS4, etc;
  • Convenient Versatility: Type C to Micro B cable not only charges devices but also transfers data. With 2A(Max) power output, charging phone faster. File transfer rate up to 480Mbps(Max) for USB 2.0 devices, backward compatibles with full speed USB 1.1 (12 Mbps) and low speed USB 1.0 (1.5 Mbps);
  • Everlasting Durability: this type c to micro usb cable with premium TPE housing and ABS contacts, which could extend its service life to a large extent and make it withstands a test of 10000+ plug and unplug. TPE housing makes the cable anti-bending, usually takes up less space and more durable. Triple shield with tinned copper plus ground wire plus Aluminum foil make sure faster data transfer without EMI (Electromagnetic Interference);

Product Description

UGREEN USB-C(Type-C) to Micro USB B cable lets you directly connect many of your standard Micro USB devices into laptops that are USB-C compatible. Usually used for connecting laptops with Android smartphones, tablets, game controllers, cameras, power banks for charging and data transfer.

Fast Charging and Syncing

With 2 A(Max) power output, the cable could charge the phone, tablet, power bank, camera faster. It could also transfer files, such as music, videos, photos and data between Type C laptop and Micro USB devices with transfer speeds up to 480 Mbps(Max).

Specification

Connector: Type C (USB C) and Micro USB (Micro B)

Wire Gauge: 28AWG

Wire Diameter: OD3.5mm

Data transfer rate: 480Mbps(Max)

Standard: USB 2.0

Core cable: tin-plated copper

Material: TPE and ABS

Cable length: 3/6 FT

USB Type-C Compatible Devices(Incomplete List)

Macbook 2015

MacBook Pro 2016

Chromebook Pixel

ASUS Zen AiO

Lenovo YOGA 900

HP Pavilion x2

HP Spectre x2

Micro USB B Compatible Devices

Samsung Galaxy Smartphones, Android Phones from other Manufacturers like Motorola, Huawei, Google, Blackberry, LG, HTC, PS4 and Xbox Controllers etc.

Important Notes

Please confirm your device is equipped with a Micro-USB port, NOT Mini-USB port.

USB C is compatible with Thunderbolt 3, NOT compatible with Thunderbolt 2.

Apple laptops need to install Android Mobile Assistant APP when transferring data between Apple laptops and Android phones.

Question:
Will this allow me to charge a usb c device from anther device with a micro usb output? or does it only work the other way around?
Answer:
As far as I know, the only USB-micro ports that offer power OUT are USB-OTG ports and those are usually only found on phones and tablets. USB OTG is not spec'd to source a lot of power, so I don't see this as a good thing to try. Most battery packs use the USB-micro port for charging the pack itself only.
